WEBVTT

00:02.200 --> 00:04.078
ANNOUNCER:
<i>In last week's episode of</i> Soap,

00:04.280 --> 00:08.354
<i>Burt checked into</i>
<i>the mental institution to try</i>
<i>and cure his invisibility,</i>

00:08.560 --> 00:11.234
<i>while Carol has lured</i>
<i>Jodie away for the weekend</i>

00:11.440 --> 00:13.830
<i>to try to put an end</i>
<i>to his homosexuality.</i>

00:14.040 --> 00:17.192
<i>Meanwhile, Prosecutor Franklin</i>
<i>has promised Judge Petrillo</i>

00:17.400 --> 00:20.916
<i>a surprise witness who will put</i>
<i>an end to Jessica.</i>

00:21.120 --> 00:25.080
<i>Confused? You won't be after</i>
<i>this week's episode of</i> Soap.

00:25.280 --> 00:27.237
[♪♪♪]

00:29.640 --> 00:32.473
<i>This is the story of two sisters:</i>

00:32.680 --> 00:35.912
<i>Jessica Tate and Mary Campbell.</i>

00:36.640 --> 00:38.632
<i>These are the Tates.</i>

00:40.160 --> 00:42.197
<i>And these are the Campbells.</i>

00:43.640 --> 00:45.677
<i>And this is</i> Soap.

00:45.880 --> 00:47.837
[♪♪♪]

00:49.960 --> 00:52.714
You son of a... Go!

00:52.920 --> 00:54.991
JESSICA:
Boys. Boys.

01:00.680 --> 01:02.637
[♪♪♪]

